WEBVTT

00:09:59.165 --> 00:10:02.499
But what if passion
has a finite shelf life?

00:10:03.624 --> 00:10:07.338
What if there are things
that even a good relationship

00:10:07.338 --> 00:10:08.743
can never provide?

00:10:10.187 --> 00:10:13.202
If even happy people cheat,

00:10:13.202 --> 00:10:14.798
what is it about?

00:10:16.765 --> 00:10:19.641
The vast majority of people
that I actually work with

00:10:19.641 --> 00:10:22.425
are not at all chronic philanderers.

00:10:22.429 --> 00:10:26.475
They are often people who are
deeply monogamous in their beliefs,

00:10:26.475 --> 00:10:28.048
and at least for their partner.

00:10:28.865 --> 00:10:31.501
But they find themselves in a conflict